name: "Princess Mononoke"
description: Work based on the character of Princess Mononoke / Mononoke, San, Princess Wolf, Girl Wolf, Princess of the Beasts. Prince Emishi Ashitaka, Moro and his cubs, Okkoto and his pack, the Spirit of the Forest and the rest of the creatures that live in it, such as the friendly Kodamas. Lady Eboshi, Jigo and their army.
